### ============================================================
### PAGINATION & FILTERING EXAMPLES
### ============================================================

### Notes with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/notes?PageNumber=1&PageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Notes with sorting (ascending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/notes?OrderBy=Subject
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Notes with sorting (descending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/notes?OrderBy=CreateDate desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Authors with pagination and sorting
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/authors?PageNumber=1&PageSize=10&OrderBy=AccountName
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Gas logs with multiple sorting fields
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/automobiles/1/gaslogs?OrderBy=Date desc,TotalPrice
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================
### ERROR HANDLING TEST CASES
### ============================================================

### Get non-existent note (should return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/notes/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get non-existent author (should return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/authors/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create note with invalid authorId (should return 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/notes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subject": "Invalid Note",
  "content": "This note has an invalid author ID",
  "authorId": 99999,
  "catalogId": 1
}

### Request without authorization (should return 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/notes

### Invalid JSON (should return 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/authors
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountName": "test",
  invalid json here
}

